          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="labelFormulaText">
            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QLabel {
    color: rgb(80, 80, 80);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", "Roboto", sans-serif;
}</string>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string>CE HIGH FREQUENCY RESPONSE

RXX = rπ + (β + 1)RX
RSB = RS || RB
RCL = RC || RL

Rπ = rπ(RSB + RX) / (RSB + RXX)
fπ = 1 / (2π Rπ Cπ)

Rµ = [RXX(RSB + RCL) + (β+1)·RSB·RCL] / (RSB + RXX)
fµ = 1 / (2π Rµ Cµ)

fπ || fµ  ≤  fH  ≤  min(fπ, fµ)
Conservative: fH = fπ || fµ</string>
            </property>
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
